strings.Value: "The cruel truth of this world has revealed itself to you. You know that the strong get the most succulent cuts, and the weak had best keep their silence. You are not blind, like the others... So what holds you back? Why don't you seize what is yours?"
"That's none of your concern, corpse. If I catch word that you're meddling in my business, all the gods in the world won't be able to dig you up."
